name: Generate an inference unit evaluation report when no report specification is given

steps.name: Given a valid, preconfigured inference unit for tabular single output regression
And a uuid my_unique_identifier for the inference unit evaluation
And an evaluation plan file for tabular regression with no evaluation tasks and no report specification
And we read the evaluation plan
When we run inference unit evaluation
Then the generated evaluation report contains a performance summary table section
Then the titles of the report and sections match the report specification in the evaluation plan
Then the specified dataset reference is in the report
Then the specified uuid is in the report

fullName: It must be possible to assess that a tabular regression inference unit behaves as intended: Generate an inference unit evaluation report when no report specification is given
